OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1772885581
OL,3,CMan charged with murder after stabbing
OL,4,Coutside Birmingham school
OL,6,FA man has been charged with murder and
OL,7,Fattempted murder following a stabbing
OL,8,Fclose to a primary school in the Alum
OL,9,FRock area of Birmingham on Tuesday 3
OL,10,FMarch.
OL,12,FWest Midlands Police were called to
OL,13,FBridge Road just after midday where
OL,14,Fthey found 30-year-old Ali Alshmari
OL,15,Fwith stab injuries. Mr Alshmari was
OL,16,Fpronounced dead at the scene a short
OL,17,Ftime later.
OL,19,FA woman in her 50s who suffered
OL,20,Finjuries to her hand, has since been
OL,21,Fdischarged from hospital.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/4
