OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1772885581
OL,3,CMan charged with murder after stabbing
OL,4,Coutside Birmingham school
OL,6,FMahmood Ibrahim, 32, of no fixed
OL,7,Faddress, has been charged with murder
OL,8,Fand attempted murder. He has been
OL,9,Fremanded in custody and is due before
OL,10,FBirmingham Magistrates Court on
OL,11,FThursday 5 March.
OL,13,FWest Midlands Police acknowledged the
OL,14,Fstabbing took place close to a school
OL,15,Fand says it has met with members of
OL,16,Fthe local community to discuss their
OL,17,Fconcerns and offer reassurance.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/4
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
