PN,37803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1772885581
OL,3,CMan charged with murder after stabbing
OL,4,Coutside Birmingham school
OL,6,FIn a statement, Det Insp Michelle
OL,7,FCordell, who is leading the
OL,8,Finvestigation, said: "This is a
OL,9,Fsignificant development in our
OL,10,Finvestigation, which is continuing.
OL,12,F"Our thoughts remain with Mr
OL,13,FAlshmari's family as we carry out our
OL,14,Fenquiries.
OL,16,F"We are grateful to the public for
OL,17,Ftheir response following this
OL,18,Fincident, and we understand the
OL,19,Fconcern it has caused.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/4
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
