PN,37804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1772885581
OL,3,CMan charged with murder after stabbing
OL,4,Coutside Birmingham school
OL,6,F"Footage shared with us has been
OL,7,Fhelpful to the investigation, and we
OL,8,Fare urging anyone who has not yet been
OL,9,Fin touch to please do so.
OL,11,F"Extra officers remain in the area,
OL,12,Fand anyone with concerns should speak
OL,13,Fto them."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/4
